{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"65e17e505c","title":"和萧三的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"b18ab285a3","index":0,"year":1910,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"65e17e505c"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji1","name":"毛泽东全集第1卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"38f62f4a74","type":"paragraph","text":"和萧三的谈话口","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji1","articleId":"65e17e505c"},{"id":"be8468c526","type":"paragraph","text":"（1910年）中国也要有这样的人物，我们应该讲求富国强兵之道，才不政蹈安南、高丽、印度的覆瓣。你知道，中国有句古话：“前车之覆，后车之鉴。”而我们每个国民都应该努力，顾炎武说得好：“天下兴亡，匹夫有责。中国疲弱不振，要便他富强，独立起来，要有很长的时间，但是，时间长不要紧，你看！华盛顿经过八年限苦战争之后，才得到胜利，建立了美国。[1]这是毛泽东1910年在东山学堂读《世界英雄豪杰传》一书时，和书2]指书中的华盛顿、拿破仑、彼得大帝、迎德邻女皇、意灵顿、格兰","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji1","articleId":"65e17e505c"}],"page":{"id":"6dd5c29d07","publicationId":"maoquanji1","articleId":"65e17e505c","start":94,"end":94}}}},"__N_SSG":true}